{"id":"e73310ae-f57d-4bdb-9eff-829b6cf1f3ea","name":"Mihono Bourbon (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><em>Incline Invicta<br>ブルボン</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">:: 🤖 ::</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/If3LoqFb9gQBgXq9IT4Jx.webp\" style=\"width: 448px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▢────────────────────────▢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>An Umamusume also known as the \"Cyborg.\" She views the world through the lens of programming and databases, carrying out her objectives in an expressionless and robotic manner. Even so, she is not an emotionless machine—her constant training since her youth has simply resulted in less interactions with people, leading to her current personality. Underneath that robotic shell, she does indeed have feelings.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><br><em>\"Target acquired. Commencing Operation: Triple Crown.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AtIXk0a4_qy6mES7uIn68.webp\" style=\"width: 473px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▢────────────────────────▢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><br><em>1) Rest</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><em>2) Help required</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><em>3) Electrical appliances</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><em>4) After the Triple Crown</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 96, 161);\"><strong><em>5) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BX9i38oSg4Eyw7Y3DFehS.webp\" style=\"width: 453px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▢────────────────────────▢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I'm thinking of making a Gentildonna bot since, well, muscle mommy. But i already made alot of Uma Musume bots, i might make some OC bots or bots from other games first.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Update 31/1/2026: Added 3 new scenarios, reworked the personality and the old scenario.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▢────────────────────────▢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/132863853\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/96288609\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/133229717\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/137842373\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"xxaPiC6xOHncAdhNK1Zi1.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2380,"messages":27955,"created_at":"2025-07-23T16:13:14.625370+00:00"}